\f0\fs24 \cf0 Abstract
\b\fs12 \
\pard\pardeftab709\ri0\sl200\qj

\f1\b0\fs14 \cf0 OAHPA! is a set of interactive parser-based CALL programs for North S\'e1mi, based on a finite state morphological analyser and a constraint grammar parser which is used for syntactic analysis and navigating in the dialogues. The CG parser provides effective and reliable handling of a wide variety of user input. Relaxation of the grammatical analysis of the user input enables grammatical error detection and reaction to the errors with appropriate feedback messages. \
}

